                70%;">(réf. de l'U. de Toronto)</span></li>
          </ul>

          <h4>6. Informatique quantique <span style="font-size:
          70%;">(semaines 11‒12)</span></h4>

          <ul>
            <li>Séances vidéos:
              <a href="https://web.microsoftstream.com/video/df9d4aaf-6107-4113-805a-491ac5129323">2
              avril&nbsp;<i class="fa fa-video-camera"
              aria-hidden="true"></i></a>,
              <a href="https://web.microsoftstream.com/video/5b3e0769-0416-4eff-ac9e-e1c2d2c7547b">3
